## Implementation Notes
- Use `#[cfg_attr(target_arch = "wasm32", wasm_bindgen)]` for conditional export
- Chainable APIs should consume and return `Self`, not `&mut Self`
- Use `JsValue` for error returns, not `Result<_, String>`
- Consider memory management - wasm_bindgen handles most cases
- Large data should use `Uint8Array` or JSON serialization
- Avoid exposing internal implementation details

